&lt;b&gt;&lt;font color="#0000FF" size="4"&gt;TRIM-POT CROSS REFERENCE&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;
&lt;P&gt;
&lt;TABLE BORDER=0 CELLSPACING=1 CELLPADDING=2&gt;
